    "Vision (image) support": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "视觉（图像）支持"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "視覺（圖像）支援"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Weights and the multimodal projector download together from Hugging Face (unsloth quantizations). Need a different model? Use Download from URL or drop a GGUF into the Models folder in the Files app.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "模型权重与多模态投影器将一起从 Hugging Face 下载（unsloth 量化版本）。需要其他模型？使用“从 URL 下载”，或将 GGUF 文件放入“文件”App 的 Models 文件夹。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "模型權重與多模態投影器將一起從 Hugging Face 下載（unsloth 量化版本）。需要其他模型？使用「從 URL 下載」，或將 GGUF 檔案放入「檔案」App 的 Models 資料夾。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "What should openTihui do?": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "openTihui 应该做什么？"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "openTihui 應該做什麼？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When the chat opens, prefill the composer with the clipboard text. After you take a screenshot, offer to attach it (tap Add) — it's never attached without your tap. Asks for Photos access. Works in normal chats and shortcuts.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "打开对话时用剪贴板文本预填输入框。截图后会提示是否附带（点按“添加”）—— 未经点按绝不会附带。需要照片访问权限。在普通对话和快捷指令中均有效。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "開啟對話時用剪貼簿文字預填輸入框。截圖後會提示是否附帶（點按「新增」）—— 未經點按絕不會附帶。需要照片存取權限。在一般對話和快捷指令中均有效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When the chat opens, prefill the composer with the clipboard text. When you send, attach a screenshot taken in the last 30 seconds (asks for Photos access). Works in normal chats and shortcuts.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "聊天打开时，用剪贴板文本预填充输入框。发送时，附上最近 30 秒内截取的截屏（需请求照片访问权限）。在普通聊天和快捷指令中均有效。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "聊天開啟時，用剪貼簿文字預填輸入框。傳送時，附上最近 30 秒內擷取的截圖（需請求照片取用權限）。在一般聊天和快捷指令中均有效。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When the window fills, the oldest middle of the chat is auto-compacted (the system prompt is kept).": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "当窗口填满时，聊天最旧的中间部分会被自动压缩（系统提示词会保留）。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "當視窗填滿時，聊天最舊的中間部分會被自動壓縮（系統提示會保留）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Works with any OpenAI-compatible API — OpenAI, OpenRouter, Groq, Together, DeepSeek, or a self-hosted llama-server / Ollama. The key is stored only on this device.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "适用于任何兼容 OpenAI 的 API — OpenAI、OpenRouter、Groq、Together、DeepSeek，或自托管的 llama-server / Ollama。密钥仅存储在此设备上。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "適用於任何相容 OpenAI 的 API — OpenAI、OpenRouter、Groq、Together、DeepSeek，或自架的 llama-server / Ollama。金鑰僅儲存在此裝置上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Write a reply to the user's message. Output only the reply.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "为用户的消息写一条回复。只输出回复内容。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "為使用者的訊息寫一則回覆。只輸出回覆內容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You are a helpful, concise assistant.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你是一个乐于助人、回答简洁的助手。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你是一個樂於助人、回答簡潔的助手。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your Shortcuts shown as chips in the keyboard, in this order. Drag to reorder, swipe to remove. Add or edit shortcuts in the Shortcuts tab.": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "你的快捷指令按此顺序在键盘中显示为按钮。拖动可重新排序，滑动可移除。在“快捷指令”标签页中添加或编辑快捷指令。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
